---
// Brand Identity section - displays the philosophy and key principles
---
<section class="mb-24">
  <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-black mb-12 border-b-2 border-primary inline-block pb-2">
    1. Brand Identity
  </h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-4 text-primary">
        The Philosophy
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Salongroei is <span class="font-bold">Friendly yet Authoritative</span>. We use soft colors, serif typography, and organic "scribble" shapes to feel approachable, but high-density data and editorial layouts to establish expertise.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-background-light p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-expert-navy/5">
      <ul class="space-y-4 font-semibold text-sm">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
          Use Serifs for Headings
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
          XL Rounded Corners (1.5rem+)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
          Color Tints for Sections
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
          Subtle Floating Accents
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
